<p><img src="/assets/rootex_editor_sponza.png" alt="Rootex Editor Sponza Screenshot" /></p>

<p><strong>Rootex Engine</strong> is an advanced 3D game engine written in C++, which is planned to support a work-in-progress game, to be released in 2021. It comes with an editor written with ImGui which uses immediate GUI.</p>

